T-stats\">{{cite web | title = Facts about Dallas Area Rapid Transit (DART) | publisher = Dallas Area Rapid Transit | url = http://www.dart.org/about/dartfacts.asp | date = February 26, 2013 | access-date = 2013-07-23}}</ref>\n| 989\n| 1996<ref name=\"DART-history\">{{cite web | title = DART.org \u2013 DART History | publisher = Dallas Area Rapid Transit | url = http://www.dart.org/about/history.asp | year = 2015 | access-date = 2015-01-12}}</ref>\n| 64<ref name=\"DART-stats\" />\n| 4<ref name=\"DART-sched\">{{cite web | title = DART.org \u2013 DART Schedules | publisher = Dallas Area Rapid Transit | url = http://www.dart.org/schedules/schedules.asp | year = 2013 | access-date = 2013-08-25}}</ref>\n| 2016<ref name=\"DART-history\" />\n|-\n| 7\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Central Link]]<ref name=\"commrail\" group=\"note\" />\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Seattle]]\n| 25,217,855<ref name=\"soundtransit.org\">{{cite report |date= |title=Third Quarter 2019 Service Delivery Quarterly Performance Report |url=https://www.soundtransit.org/sites/default/files/documents/service-delivery-performance-report-q3-2019_0.pdf |format=PDF |publisher=[[Sound Transit]] | access-date=2019-06-11}}</ref>\n| 79,113<ref name=\"soundtransit.org\" />\n| {{convert|20.4|mi|km}}<ref name=\"SoundTransit-sched\">{{cite web | title = Schedules \u2013 SoundTransit | publisher = Sound Transit | url = http://www.soundtransit.org/Schedules | year = 2016 | access-date = 2016-03-29}}</ref>\n| 3,878\n| 2009\n| 16<ref name=\"SoundTransit-sched\" />\n| 1<ref name=\"SoundTransit-sched\" />\n| 2016<ref name=\"Beekman\">{{cite news|url=https://www.seattletimes.com/seattle-news/transportation/angle-lake-station-opens-saturday-with-celebration/|title=Angle Lake Station Opens Saturday with celebration|last=Lindblom|first=Mike|date=September 22, 2016|newspaper=[[The Seattle Times]]|access-date=2017-11-02}}</ref>\n|-\n| 8\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Regional Transportation District|Denver RTD]]:<ref