20616134732/http://www.gohrt.com/services/the-tide | archive-date = 2012-06-16 | url-status = dead }}</ref>\n| 568\n| 2011<ref name=\"Norfolk-open\">{{cite web|title=Light Rail Service to Begin August 19, 2011 |publisher=Hampton Roads Transit |url=http://www.gohrt.com/light-rail-service-to-begin-august-19-2011/ |access-date=2013-08-10 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102224455/http://www.gohrt.com/light-rail-service-to-begin-august-19-2011/ |archive-date=2014-01-02 }}</ref>\n| 11<ref name=\"Norfolk\" />\n| 1<ref name=\"Norfolk\" />\n| n/a\n|-\n| 32\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[QLine|Q-Line]]\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Detroit]]\n| 1,200,000<ref name=\"qline\">{{cite web | url = https://www.bridgemi.com/detroit-journalism-cooperative/qline-well-short-ridership-goals-and-plagued-delays-detroit | title = QLine well short of ridership goals and plagued by delays in Detroit | publisher = Bridge | date = April 1, 2019 | access-date = 2016-06-11}}</ref>\n| 3,288<ref name=\"daily-ave\" group=\"note\" /><ref name=\"qline\" />\n|{{convert|3.3|mi|km}}\n| 996\n|2017\n|20\n|1\n|n/a\n|-\n| 33\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[DC Streetcar]]\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Washington, D.C.]]\n| 1,093,400\n| 2,400\n| {{convert|2.4|mi|km}}\n| 1,000\n| 2016\n| 8\n| 1\n| n/a\n|-\n| 34\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Tacoma Link]]<ref group=\"note\" name=\"commrail\" />\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Tacoma, Washington|Tacoma]]\n| 909,429<ref name=\"soundtransit.org\" />\n| 2,990<ref name=\"soundtransit.org\" />\n| {{convert|1.6|mi|km}}<ref name=\"SoundTransit-sched\" />\n| 1,869\n| 2003\n| 5<ref name=\"SoundTransit-sched\" />\n| 1<ref name=\"SoundTransit-sched\" />\n| n/a<ref name=\"Beekman\" />\n|-\n| 35\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[TECO Line Streetcar System|TECO Line Streetcars]]<ref group=\"note\" name=\"heritage\" />\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Tampa, Florida|Tampa]]\n| 902,700\n| 2,400\n| {{convert|2.7|mi|km}}<ref name=